Class Rectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shape
      • Rectangle
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Square

    public class Rectangle
extends Shape
    A Rectangle is a Shape which maintains information about its height and width. A Rectangle knows how to return and set its height and width, calculates and return its area, calculate and return its perimeter, and calculate and return its diagonal.
